summary: Adaptable, analytical and enthusiastic financial economics professional with a passion for the fusion between strategic investments, technology and social finance. Convinced that we are work in progress from cradle to grave, I enjoy the bandwidth to grow and experiment with new projects, ideas and responsibilities. Strong analytical skills coupled with emotional intelligence is my not-so-secret recipe to interact successfully with clients and colleagues. Fintech-enthusiast and knowledge craver. A strong "buck stops here" approach to business and getting things done. Always on the look-out to redesign life to fulfill our (wildest) dreams.
